                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171029-58-defend394 t18171029-58-punish316"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 31.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Park.</p>
